      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Adajus Jeroaima Dehls/ ta Dehla Paſur/ ta Deh-\nla Malkija / un Maësajus Adi-\nela Dehls/ ta Dehla Jaſsera/ ta\nDehla Mesullama / ta Dehla\nMesillemita/ Immera Dehla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta patt winnu Brahti/\nkawn Tehwn Nammu Wirfnee-\nki tubkfſtochi feptinxſintg un fesch-\ndefmits ſtipri warreni Wihri /\npee ta Deewa Namuna Amma-\nta Darba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no teem Lewiteem no\nMetaza Behrneem : Semajus\nAsuba Dehls/ ta Dehla Asrika-\nma/ ta Dehla Asabija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Bakbakars tas Nem-\nmesis/ un Galals/ un Matani-\njus Mika Dehls/ ta Dehla Sik-\nri Affawa Dehla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Obadjus tas Dehls\nSemaja/ ta Dehla Gelala/ Je-\ndutuxa Dehla : Un Berekijus\nAffawa Dehls ta Dehla Elkana/\nkas to Netowatiteru Zeemds\ndsihwuja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Wahrtu-Sargi\nbija: Sallums un Akubs/ un\nTalinons/ un Afimans ar fa-\nweem Brahteem/ un Sallums\nbija par Wirfneeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo lihdſſchint btja ſchee\nWahrtu-Sargi pee ta Kehnina\nWahrtim prett Rihteem ſtarp\nLewja Behrnu Lehgereein.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sallums Kore Dehls/\nta Dehla Abi Ahawa / ta Dehla\nKorus/ ar faweem Brahteem ne\nfawa Tehwa Namma/ tee Ko-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "riterti bija pahr to Ammata Dar-\nbu / par Sleegtau-Sargeem\nDsihwokli/ itt ka winnu Tehwi\nta KUNGA Lehgeri bijufchi/ to\nee-eijamn Weetu fargadami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Pineas Eeleasara\nDehls bija zittkahrt par Wirf-\nneeku pahr teeni/ ar ko tas\nKUNGS bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakarijas Meselemija\nDehls bija par Wahrtu-Sargu\npee tahs Sa-eefchanas Telts\nDurwim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi/ kas par Sleegtau-\nSargeemi bija eezelti/ bija diwi-\nfints un diwipadeſmits/ tee bt-\nja lihdſſinati pehz faweem Zee-\nmeem. Dahwidg un Samuels\ntas Redsetajs bij tohs fawa Am-\nmatā eezehtufchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tee ar faweem Behr-\nneem par Sargeem buhtu ta\nKUNGA Namma pee tahs\nTelts Namma/ ka tee to fargatu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Sargi bija prett\nteem tfchetreem Wehjeem likti/\nprett Rihteem / prett Wakkara-\npuffi/ prett Seemetapuffi / un\nprett Deenas-Widduspuffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnu Brahti bija\nfawds Zeemds / ka tee feptita\nDeena allasch eenahktu / un ar\nteem kalpotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee Lewiti bij ſcheem\ntfchetradeem Sargu-Wirfnee-\nkeem ustizzeti/ un tee bija pahr\nteem Schkirsteem un Deewa\nNamna Mantahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee palifke zaur Nafti\napkahrt to Deewa Namnu/ jo\nGgggg 3 teem\n"
    }
  ],
